{"tid":2426125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二二八74週年","createTime":"2021-02-27T22:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T10:31:34.000Z","uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26ff11b2656464f0b2e87c1b60e8d7947450e462","tid":2426125,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T22:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%85%AB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6#/media/File:228_Incident_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%2585%25AB%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%3A228_Incident_h.jpg&h=7d2a80c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>二二八事件是臺灣於1947年2月27日至5月16日發生的事件。1947年2月27日，因專賣局查緝員在臺北市查緝私菸時不當使用公權力造成民眾死傷，引起28（次）日的陳抗傷亡，更擴及後續臺灣民眾大規模反抗政府與攻佔官署，本省人對外省人報復攻擊，國民政府派遣軍隊逮捕與鎮壓殺害臺灣民眾。此事件，造成民眾大量的傷亡。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.228.org.tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.228.org.tw%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3qkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=8637106f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.228.org.tw/</a>"},{"pid":"91d351a1fe8e339147a64abad3fbd09fbc04fd05","tid":2426125,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T22:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://takao.tw/wp-content/uploads/20170127153952_68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftakao.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20170127153952_68.jpg&h=7a71f362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfbc3ccab97c2548478b036931477ee3bbfeddc5","tid":2426125,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T22:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20210221/1139x768_20210221000041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20210221%2F1139x768_20210221000041.jpg&h=60cd9ae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55e51b9f15fd3aa0319348ca